e a 51 Vicar offer me a rez out of the blue, after I had made my way all the way back from SQeynos to LGuk zone ent, LoL.  She then offered to pull the AHand, and to Gate, allowing my heart-pounding Wizard to say a quick prayer, then jump behind the Hand, swim up, grab the Rod (still with the Inv vs Undead she gave me), jump back in the water, and Gate my way back to Sqeynos.  Mission accomplished, and she still receives &quot;Thank you!&quot;s to this day for such a display of compassion for a young player.  My experience showed me that most Druids/Wizards/anyone elseare perfectly willing to help a young guy out, who is going for a quest that is a bit over his head-just be nice as possible when you /ooc, or approach a Druid Ring and request help.  NOTE: You might want to find some extra Fish Scales, as they are needed for any Endure Breath spells that might be given to you!  To end my comments-in total, of buying potions, and donating for TPs/SoWs/Invs/Inv vs Undeads, etc., this Staff cost me a grand total of not more than 100pp.  That comes to an astounding price of 10pp per Int.  Not bad, considering my little level 11 lost only one life during the entirety of the quest.  Only takes a few hours, too, if you are lucky.  Good luck-only thing I would change, would be to have done the quest as soon as I dinged 4 and got Gate.  Being an Erudite, had I known earlier, I would have gotten the two Rods from Erud's Xing and SQey at level 1!  Please post, anyone who has completed the quest at a lower level than 11-curious to know if I hold the record, if even for a little while. hehehe!  See you guys at Crow's!<br>
     Haile Selassie, 12th level Wizard of the Eruditian Council <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm24.showMessage?topicID=24.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm24.showMessage?topicID=16.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm24.emailToFriend?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm24.threadControl?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm24.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm24.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizar